I"<p>10種最常用的Excel公式</p>

<p>1、邏輯判斷</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>=IF(A2="試用期",200,IF(B2&gt;=5,1000,500))
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><img src="/images/posts/Execl/p101.png" /></p>

<p>2、複雜條件邏輯判斷</p>

<p>女 60 , 男 65 退休</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>=IF((A2="女")*(B2&gt;=60)+(A2="男")*(B2&gt;=65),"退休","")
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><img src="/images/posts/Execl/p102.png" /></p>

<p>3、匯總求和</p>

<p>60 以上的總合</p>

<p>=SUMIF(B2:B8,”&gt;60”)</p>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;img src="/images/posts/Execl/p103.png"&gt;
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>4、多表合併匯總</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>=SUM(SUMIF(A2:A8,{"男","女"},B2:B8))
</code></pre></div></div>
<p><img src="/images/posts/Execl/p104.png" /></p>

<p>5、查找引用</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>=VLOOKUP(F2,A2:D8,2,0)
</code></pre></div></div>

<p><img src="/images/posts/Execl/p105.png" /></p>

